  <Method>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Spinach%20Salad_20250814_174412.jpg">Assemble ingredients.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Spinach%20Salad_20250814_181748.jpg">In a skillet over low heat, whisk vinegar, garlic, brown sugar, mustard and seasonings with bacon drippings.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Spinach%20Salad_20250814_181859.jpg">Place spinach, onion and bacon in a large warm bowl. Toss with warm dressing. </Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Spinach%20Salad_20250814_182010.jpg">Once the spinach begins to wilt, serve with sliced boiled eggs.</Step>
  </Method>
  <Variations>
    <Variation>Add &lt;a href='/GetRecipe?recipeName=Croutons'&gt;croutons&lt;/a&gt;, if desired.</Variation>
  </Variations>
